title: Patrice Carteron

title: Umm Salal SC - Wikipedia
snippet: Umm Salal were formed in 1979 under the name Al-Tadamun Club and entered into the Qatari Second Division along with five other clubs. After the dissolution of two other clubs in the second division, Al Tadamun was also dissolved. The club was reformed in 1996, with Sheikh Abdulaziz bin Abdulrahman Al Thani heading the club.

title: Learn Patrice Beaumelle facts for kids
snippet: Patrice Amir Beaumelle, born on April 24, 1978, is a French football coach and former player. He is currently the head coach of the Qatari football club Umm Salal.
